agency_desc: National voluntary nonprofit health foundation dedicated to preventing, treating, and curing hepatitis and all liver diseases through research, education, and support groups.
service_description: Provides information, support, and advocacy for those affected by hepatitis and other liver-related diseases. Maintains a listing of local support groups, clinical trials, and transplant information.
site_details: Call or visit the website for more information.
